-- Venezuela will not recognize World Bank ruling in Exxon case
-- 
-- Sun Jan 8, 2012 2:18pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/01/08/us-venezuela-exxonmobil-chavez-idUSTRE8070KY20120108

 

 CARACAS  (Reuters) - Venezuelan President Hugo Chavez said on Sunday that his country would not recognize a ruling by a World Bank tribunal in a multibillion-dollar arbitration case with Exxon Mobil Corp ( XOM.N ). 
 "I tell you: we will not recognize any decision," Chavez said during a televised speech. (Reporting by  Daniel Wallis ; Editing by  Eric Beech )